---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us | SMS API Compare"
  description="Get in touch with SMS API Compare for questions, feedback, advertising inquiries, or partnership opportunities."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Contact Us</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      We'd love to hear from you. Whether you have a question, feedback, or a business inquiry, reach out using the appropriate channel below.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">General Inquiries</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        For questions, feedback, or corrections, email us at
        <a href="mailto:contact@smsapicompare.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@smsapicompare.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Advertising & Sponsorship</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Interested in advertising on SMS API Compare or exploring sponsorship opportunities? Contact our advertising team at
        <a href="mailto:advertise@smsapicompare.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">advertise@smsapicompare.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Are You an SMS API Provider?</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        We'd love to ensure your data is accurate. If you represent an SMS API provider and notice any outdated or incorrect information on our site, please let us know. We're committed to keeping our comparisons fair and up to date.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        You can submit corrections or updates directly through our
        <a href="https://github.com/sms-api-compare/sms-api-compare" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub repository</a>,
        or email us at
        <a href="mailto:contact@smsapicompare.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@smsapicompare.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Response Time</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        We typically respond within 1-2 business days. Thank you for your patience.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
